[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me, \u201c<st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Even if</st> <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> and <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stood</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> me pleading for<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">I</st> would <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">not</st> feel pity <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> them!<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">Get</st> them <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">away</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">me</st>! Tell them to <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">go away</st>!<n id=\"4\" />",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">If</st> they <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">ask</st> you, \u2018<st data-num=\"0575\" class=\"\">Where</st> should we <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">go</st>?\u2019 <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">tell</st> them the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">this</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018Those <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> are destined to <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">die of disease</st> will go to <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">death by disease</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Those <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> are destined to die in <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">war</st> will go to death in <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">war</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Those <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> are destined to die of <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">starvation</st> will go to death by <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">starvation</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Those <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> are destined to go into <st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">exile</st> will go into <st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">exile</st>.\u2019<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"06485 05921\">punish</st> them in <st data-num=\"0702\" class=\"\">four</st> different <st data-num=\"04940\" class=\"\">ways</st>: I will have <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">war</st> <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">kill</st> them; I will have <st data-num=\"03611\" class=\"\">dogs</st> <st data-num=\"05498\" class=\"\">drag off</st> their dead bodies; I will have <st data-num=\"05775 08064\">birds</st> and <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">wild</st> <st data-num=\"0929\" class=\"\">beasts</st> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">devour</st> and <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> their corpses.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "I will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> all the people in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdoms</st> of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">world</st> <st data-num=\"02113\" class=\"\">horrified</st> <st data-num=\"01558\" class=\"\">at</st> what has happened to them <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because of</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> <st data-num=\"03169\">Hezekiah\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st>, <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> cried out,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">in the world</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"02550\" class=\"\">have pity</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> you, <st data-num=\"03389\">Jerusalem</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> will <st data-num=\"05110\" class=\"\">grieve</st> over you?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> will <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">stop</st> long enough<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"07592\" class=\"\">inquire</st> about <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">how</st> you <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">are doing</st>?<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I, the <st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\"><span class=\"\"smcaps\"\">Lord</span></st>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">say</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> people have <st data-num=\"05203\" class=\"\">deserted</st> me;<p class=\"poetry\">you keep <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">turning</st> your <st data-num=\"0268\" class=\"\">back</st> on me.\u2019<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">So I have <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">unleashed</st> my <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">power</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> you<n id=\"3\" /> and have begun to <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> you.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"03811\" class=\"\">grown tired</st> of <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">feeling sorry for</st> you!\u201d<n id=\"5\" /></p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> continued,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cIn every <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">town</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> I will <st data-num=\"02219\" class=\"\">purge</st> them <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04214\" class=\"\">like straw blown away by the wind</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">destroy</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">kill off</st> their <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">children</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will do so because they did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">change</st> their <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">behavior</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">widows</st> will <st data-num=\"06105\" class=\"\">become</st> in my sight more <st data-num=\"06105\" class=\"\">numerous</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">than the <st data-num=\"02344\">grains of sand</st> on the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">seashores</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">At <st data-num=\"06672\" class=\"\">noontime</st> I will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> a <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyer</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> the <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mothers</st> of <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">their</st> <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will cause <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">anguish</st><n id=\"3\" /> and <st data-num=\"0928\" class=\"\">terror</st><p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall</st> <st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">suddenly</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">upon</st> them.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">mother</st> who had <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st> children<n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"0535\" class=\"\">grow faint</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">All the <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">breath</st> will <st data-num=\"05301\" class=\"\">go out</st> of her.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Her pride and joy will be taken from her in the prime of their life.<p class=\"poetry\">It will seem as if the <st data-num=\"08121\" class=\"\">sun</st> had <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">set</st> while it was <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">still</st> <st data-num=\"03119\" class=\"\">day</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">She will <st data-num=\"0954 02659\">suffer</st> <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">shame</st> and <st data-num=\"02659\" class=\"\">humiliation</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">cause</st> <st data-num=\"07611\" class=\"\">any</st> of them <st data-num=\"07611\" class=\"\">who are still left alive</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">to be killed</st> in <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">war</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">by the onslaughts</st> of their <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>,\u201d<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0188\" class=\"\">Oh</st>, <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mother</st>, <st data-num=\"0188\" class=\"\">how</st> I <st data-num=\"0188\" class=\"\">regret</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> you ever <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">gave birth</st> to me!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">I</st> am always starting <st data-num=\"07379\" class=\"\">arguments</st> and <st data-num=\"04066\" class=\"\">quarrels</st> with the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">people</st> of this <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05383\" class=\"\">lent money</st> to anyone, and I have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05383\" class=\"\">borrowed</st> from anyone.<p class=\"poetry\">Yet <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> these people are <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">treating</st> me <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">with contempt</st>.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\"><span class=\"\"smcaps\"\">Lord</span></st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cJerusalem,<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"0518 03808\">surely</st> <st data-num=\"08281\" class=\"\">send</st> you <st data-num=\"08281\" class=\"\">away</st> for your own <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"0518 03808\">surely</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06293\" class=\"\">bring</st> the <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st> <st data-num=\"06293\" class=\"\">upon</st> you in a <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> of <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">trouble</st> and <st data-num=\"06869\" class=\"\">distress</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Can you people who are like <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st> and <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">break</st> that <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st> fist from the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">give away</st> your <st data-num=\"02428\" class=\"\">wealth</st> and your <st data-num=\"0214\" class=\"\">treasures</st> as <st data-num=\"0957\" class=\"\">plunder</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will give it away <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">free</st> of <st data-num=\"04242\" class=\"\">charge</st> for the <st data-num=\"03605 02403\">sins</st> you have committed <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">throughout</st> your <st data-num=\"01366\" class=\"\">land</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will make you <st data-num=\"05647\">serve</st> your <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st><n id=\"1\" /> in a <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> that you <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">nothing</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">about</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> my <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st> is like a <st data-num=\"0784 06919\">fire</st> that will <st data-num=\"03344\" class=\"\">burn</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> you.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> how I suffer.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">Take thought of</st> me and <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">care for</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05358\" class=\"\">Pay back</st> for me those who have been <st data-num=\"07291\" class=\"\">persecuting</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0750 0639\">be</st> so <st data-num=\"0750 0639\">patient</st> with them that you allow them to <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">kill</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">Be mindful of</st> how I have <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">put up</st> with their <st data-num=\"02781\" class=\"\">insults</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> your <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">sake</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">As your <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">came</st> to me, I <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">drank</st> them <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">in</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">they</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">filled</st> my <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">heart</st> with <st data-num=\"08342\" class=\"\">joy</st> and <st data-num=\"08057\" class=\"\">happiness</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">belong</st> to <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">you</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> O <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">spend</st> my <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">time</st> in the <st data-num=\"05475\" class=\"\">company</st> of other people,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07832\" class=\"\">laughing</st> and <st data-num=\"05937\" class=\"\">having a good time</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">stayed</st> <st data-num=\"0910\" class=\"\">to myself</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">because</st> I <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">felt obligated</st> to you<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> I was <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">filled</st> with <st data-num=\"02195\" class=\"\">anger</st> at what they had done.</p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> must I <st data-num=\"05331\" class=\"\">continually</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">suffer</st> such <st data-num=\"03511\" class=\"\">painful anguish</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Why must I endure the <st data-num=\"0605\" class=\"\">sting</st> of their insults like an <st data-num=\"03985 07495\">incurable</st> <st data-num=\"04347\" class=\"\">wound</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Will you <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">let</st> me <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">down</st> when I need you,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03644\" class=\"\">like</st> a <st data-num=\"0391 04325\">brook one goes to for water</st> but that <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">be relied on</st>?\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Because of this</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">said</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cYou must <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">repent</st> of such words and thoughts!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> you do, I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">restore</st> you to the privilege of <st data-num=\"06440 05975\">serving</st> me.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> you <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">say</st> <st data-num=\"03368\" class=\"\">what is worthwhile</st> instead of <st data-num=\"02151\" class=\"\">what is worthless</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">I will again allow you to <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> my <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">spokesman</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">They</st> must <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">become</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">as</st> you have been.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> must <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">become</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">like</st> them.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> you as strong as a <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">wall</st> to <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"01219\" class=\"\">fortified</st> wall of <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03898 0413\">attack</st> you,<p class=\"poetry\">but they will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">be able to overcome</st> you.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will be <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> you to <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">rescue</st> you and <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">deliver</st> you,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">deliver</st> you from the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">power</st> of the <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wicked</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06299\" class=\"\">free</st> you from the <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">clutches</st> of <st data-num=\"06184\" class=\"\">violent people</st>.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "21"
  }
]